            What is fake news and how can you identify it?
            Fake news can sometimes very closely mimic real news. Zoe Kleinman reports on on how to to spot it.This is part of a series by the BBC on disinformation and fake news - a global problem challenging the way we share information and perceive the world around us.To see more stories and learn more about the series visit www.bbc.co.uk/fakenews
                
